    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">significant</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Neural Assembly</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to trigger node growth and begin the <VAL_ON>grafting process<>.<br><br>Each node is genetically unique, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Improves <span class=\"name name-stellar\">take-off efficiency</span>.",
