    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">神經電路板</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">重大</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 觸發節點生長，並開始<VAL_ON>移植程序<>。<br><br>每個節點的基因皆不相同，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">起飛效率</span>。"
